ISLAMABAD, Apr 22 (APP): Rabia Naseem Farooqi on Monday took oath as a Member of the National Assembly (MNA) and Speaker Sardar Ayaz Sadiq administered the oath to her, who later signed the registration roll.
The Election Commission of Pakistan on April 17, 2024 notified Rabia Naseem Farooqi from PML-N as a returned candidate for the seat reserved for women in the National Assembly from Punjab Province.
